<MELItem itemNbr="21-43-03" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-43-03.1.2-21-43-03">
<Title>Forward Cargo Heat Electric Heater</Title>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="21-43-03-02">
<Title>787-9 (VN-A861, VN-A862, VN-A863, VN-A864, VN-A865, VN-A866, VN-A867, VN-A868, VN-A869, VN-A870, VN-A871)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the inoperative forward cargo heater (AMM DDG 21-43-03).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For heater 1 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO 	ELEMENT 1.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO 	ELEMENT 2.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For heater 2 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 1.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 2.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to inoperative forward cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to inoperative forward cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>FCAC will operate normally, but will provide cooling only. Temperature sensitive
cargo that requires heating should not be carried in the forward cargo compartment.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELSubItem>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="21-43-03-03">
<Title>787-10 (VN-A872, VN-A873, VN-A874, VN-A877, VN-A878, VN-A879)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="3" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the inoperative forward cargo heater (AMM DDG 21-43-03).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For heater 1 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO 	ELEMENT 1.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO 	ELEMENT 2.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For heater 2 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 1.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 2.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For heater 3 inoperative:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 3-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 1.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 3-FWD CARGO	 ELEMENT 2.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to inoperative forward cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to inoperative forward cargo heater.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>For one, two, or all three electric heaters inoperative, FCAC will operate normally, but will provide cooling only. Temperature sensitive cargo that requires heating should not be carried in the forward cargo compartment. Refer the flight NOTOC for details.</Para>
<Para />
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELSubItem>
</MELItem>
